title: Version 1.2.0
body:
CHANGELOG:
- RGB color can be specified with the introduction of ansi_term.
- The structure of Config file was changed. (BREAKING CHANGE: Please
regenerate an `almel.yaml`)
- Improve the error handling not to crash the program.

title: Display wire separator when adjacent segments are the same color
Change not to display "git_user" segment when git user.name is not specified
body:
```sh
(almel prompt $) git config --unset user.name
config value 'user.name' was not found; class=Config (7); code=NotFound (-3)
(almel prompt $)
```

title: Change directory structures of the config module
Fix the directory segment in the root
